| accessdate = 2017-07-19}}&lt;/ref&gt; explaining that the quotation originally came from Robert J. Hanlon of [[Scranton, Pennsylvania]], as a submission (credited in print) for a compilation of various jokes related to [[Murphy's law|Murphy's Law]] that were published in [[Arthur Bloch]]'s ''Murphy's Law Book Two: More Reasons Why Things Go Wrong!'' (1980).&lt;ref name=murphytwo&gt;{{cite book
